data.description: Welcome to Bridge Harbor, one of the newest & popular communities on this side of town. This community is 5 mins to TAFB and 20 mins from either Mexico Beach or Panama City Beach. This 4/2 home is only 1 and 1/2 years old and the most sought after Cali floor plan. It features a long hallway opening up to the kitchen, dining,  and living room . Kitchen features walk in pantry and a spacious island for entertaining . There's vinyl flooring throughout but bedrooms are carpeted. Master bathroom features big walk in closet , double vanity, separate shower and garden tub. Back has a covered patio for grilling or relaxing with pond view behind and is fenced. Home has smart home package that includes, IQ Panel, smart doorbell, smart thermostat , & kwikset keyless entry. Does not require flood insurance. *Community features : Beautiful Community Pool area with BBQ grills, pavilions, tree park area, & walking access to the bay in the back of neighborhood .
